<kos/Resource/LifecycleState/InUse> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "In Use Lifecycle State"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/Resource/LifecycleState> .
<kos/Resource/LifecycleState/Decommissioned> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Decommissioned Lifecycle State"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/Resource/LifecycleState> .

# KOS Concepts for Notification Severity
<Notification/Severity/PerceivedSeverity/Critical> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Critical Perceived Severity"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/Notification/Severity/PerceivedSeverity> .
<Notification/Severity/PerceivedSeverity/Major> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Major Perceived Severity"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/Notification/Severity/PerceivedSeverity> .
<Notification/Severity/PerceivedSeverity/Minor> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Minor Perceived Severity"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/Notification/Severity/PerceivedSeverity> .
<Notification/Severity/PerceivedSeverity/Warning> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Warning Perceived Severity"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/Notification/Severity/PerceivedSeverity> .

# KOS Concepts for Agent Contact Method
<kos/org/agent-contact-method/Email> a skos:Concept ; rdfs:label "Email Contact Method"@en ; skos:inScheme <https://w3id.org/noria/kos/org/agent-contact-method> .
