:TroubleTicket_WebServerPerf_TT002 a noria:TroubleTicket ;
    rdfs:label "Customer Portal Web Server Performance Issue"@en, "Problème de Performance Serveur Web Portail Client"@fr ;
    rdfs:comment "Customers reporting slow response times on the Customer Portal. High CPU usage observed on web01.portal.example.com."@en ;
